==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bùzhī zhĕ bù zuì

===Etymology===
Literally: The one who does not know is not guilty.
===Proverb===
'''[[不知]][[者]][[不]][[罪]]'''.
# If one does not know any better, one cannot be held responsible.
